            "properties": [
                [
                    "name",
                    "Hive Ransomware"
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "Hive's proprietary encryptor — originally written in Go, later rewritten in Rust for improved performance and evasion — encrypts files across local drives and network shares, appends victim-specific extensions, and drops ransom notes with links to the Hive leak site. Deployed after data exfiltration to maximise double-extortion leverage. VSS and backup deletion commands are executed immediately before encryption to prevent recovery."
                ],
